<div><head>《湘中記羅含》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.2">《水經注》引二事：<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.3">湘水之出于陽朔則觴為之舟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.4">至洞庭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.5">日月若出入于其中也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.6">《湘水注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.7">屈潭之左有玉笥山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.8">道士遺言此福地也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-1a.9">《湘水注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.2">《後漢書郡國志》昭注引一事：<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.3">有營水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.4">有桃水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.5">有雍水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.6">有祁水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.7">有宜水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.8">有舂水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.9">有烝水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.10">有表水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.11">有耒水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.12">有淥水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.13">有漣水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.14">有瀏水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.15">有溈水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.16">有汨水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.17">有資水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.18">皆注湘。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-2a.19">《零陵郡注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.2">《初學記》引三事：<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.3">衡山遙望如陣雲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.4">沿湘千里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.5">九向九背。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.6">卷五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.7">衡山、九疑皆有舜廟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.8">太守至官，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.9">常遣戶曹致敬候祀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.10">則如有絃歌之聲。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-3a.11">卷五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.2">衡山有懸泉滴瀝嵓閒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.3">聲泠泠如絃音，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.4">有鶴迴翔其上如舞。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.5">卷五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.6">《太平御覽》引二事：<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.7">石燕在零雲縣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.8">雷風則群飛翩翩然，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.9">其土人來採有乾者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.10">今合藥或用。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-4a.11">卷四十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-5a.2">石鷰在泉陵縣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-5a.3">雷雨則群飛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-5a.4">然其土人稀有見者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1708_CHANT_001-5a.5">卷一百七十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
